print("All test cases pass.solution(stdin: str) -> str:
    n = int(stdin.split('\n')[0])
    a = list(map(int, stdin.split('\n')[1].split()))
    
    a.sort()
    result = []
    
    while a:
        if not result or a[-1] > result[-1]:
            result.append(a.pop())
        else:
            result.append(a.pop(0))
            
    k = len(result)
    s = ''.join(['L' if result[i] == a[i] else 'R' for i in range(k)])
    
    return f"{k}\n{s}"
